Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Welcome to this luxurious estate in Rattray Marsh, Mississauga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}As you step inside, a grand foyer greets you with elegance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Look at that sweeping staircase and stunning coffered ceilings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The living spaces are expansive, featuring custom millwork and wainscotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine cooking in this chef&apos;s kitchen with high-end appliances.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Gather around the oversized island, perfect for family and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The family room showcases a floor-to-ceiling gas fireplace, truly breathtaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Step into the indoor swimming pool area, designed for year-round fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Ascend to the Owners Suite, a private retreat with a luxurious ensuite.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Thank you for joining me on this remarkable tour; your dream home awaits!
